rComments: Best seminar I had in this semester. It´s really interesting; I can only recommend to take this class no matter what major you are studying

Most disorganized prof I've ever had. Never stuck to the syllabus and went on long tangents about how she doesn't know how to use the copier, or couldn't find the video that we were supposed to watch in class. Very nosy about students personal lives and likes to tell a lot of stories. You finish this module not really knowing anything new.

Dr. Reissing best prof I ever had. Supportive,passionate, full of knowledge and scientific. Best course I have taken until now and I give the full credits to Dr. Reissing. I feel fortunate for having the University of Ottawa giving me this opportunity to take this course with one of the best leaders in the field of psychology; Dr. Reissing.

this was her first time teaching the human sexual behaviours class, and I thought she did it really well. She is passionate about the field, and has a background in sex therapy. I would take another class with her if she taught one. Helpful prof. her accent can be hard to understand at times, but not usually. Interesting stories for the material.
